README for LuaJIT for devkitPPC 2.1.0-beta3
-------------------------------------------

LuaJIT is a Just-In-Time (JIT) compiler for the Lua programming language.

This repo contains some patches that enable LuaJIT to build on devkitPPC-supported platforms (currently only the Wii and GameCube).

Thanks to:
* thenumbernine for his Wii LuaJIT build script: https://github.com/thenumbernine/wii-luajit/blob/master/luajit.make.wii.sh
* p-sam for his LuaJIT build script: https://github.com/retronx-team/love-nx/blob/develop/build.sh

These scripts were used as references for the devkitPPC build script.

LuaJIT Project Homepage: https://luajit.org/

LuaJIT is Copyright (C) 2005-2022 Mike Pall.
LuaJIT is free software, released under the MIT license.
See full Copyright Notice in the COPYRIGHT file or in luajit.h.

Documentation for LuaJIT is available in HTML format.
Please point your favorite browser to:

 doc/luajit.html

